item.title: CVE-2022-4786|2024-08-03T01:48:40.432Z -- unknown -- video.js
item.description: The Video.js WordPress plugin through 4.5.0 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
